snippet.title: Longplay of The Lord of the Rings: Aragorn's Quest
snippet.description:
Longplay of The Lord of the Rings: Aragorn's Quest, played on the PlayStation Portable. This game's version was released on Sep. 14th, 2010. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!
